<head>校勘記</head>
<p>
<app from="#beg0061006" to="#end0061006"><lem wit="#wit1">一</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">十一</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0061008" to="#end0061008"><lem wit="#wit1">升</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit5">昇</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0061009" to="#end0061009"><lem wit="#wit1">讀</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit3 #wit5">讚</rdg></app>
<app cb:word-count="124" from="#beg0061007" to="#end0061007"><lem wit="#wit1"><item>無垢山居女人庇雨其舍眾仙稱穢<note n="0061008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig">升＝昇【宮】下同</note><app n="0061008"><lem wit="#wit1">升</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit5">昇</rdg></app>空<lb n="0061b09" ed="T"/>自證一</item>
<lb n="0061b10" ed="T"/><item>慧王以百味飯化人入道二</item>
